Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'The Punishing Virus concentration here is way lower than the danger threshold...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "I've never seen anything like this in all my years serving on the surface.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: '...If this desert holds the secret of an "antigen" to the virus, then it made sense that Babylonia would create a joint operation here in such short notice.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Is there really an antigen? Are we... going to take back Earth?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'The value of this antigen is... immeasurable.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: '...But my mission is to save the commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: 'Each of the Gray Ravens is a capable fighter. With them there... perhaps the commandant is not in as dire a danger as we thought.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: 'As a member of Purifying Force, I take orders from Commander Nikola. That means taking back Earth is not our only objective.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "But... standing here now, the antigen that can save Earth is within my arm's reach.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "The Purifying Force's job is to follow orders, no questions asked.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "And I'm ordered to rescue the Commandant, at any cost.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bianca', 3: "We'll only get the samples if we can.", 4: '1'}
